{"tid":1454044,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"8. 11晚上10點左右，機場都有大陸人襲擊和平示威者。","createTime":"2019-08-12T06:00:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T06:18:43.000Z","uid":268927,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2a6726c7d3e34d64e21f10e6f4fc1aff7f2f3412","tid":1454044,"uid":268927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:00:37.000Z","msg":"呢個心口有中國季的男人，懷疑喝用過的內地牌子的水，系離境個層天橋，倒水落下面，下面大把人坐系咗到。<br />\n<br />\n然後一大堆在場人士上去指駡佢，叫佢道歉，和條女分手。<br />\n<br />\n之後過咗一段時間藍衣，警察出現。<br />\n<br />\n想問下，有無媒體報道，有人知唔知佢地有無比人拘捕，我留咗一陣就無跟，落咗下面，唔知之後點。<br />\n<br />\n同場還有<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jvaQvur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjvaQvur.jpg&h=b4948518&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一堆相信系<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BxhZ8f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBxhZ8f8.jpg&h=a3a4c511&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n追緊EXO 的女仔，打扮成韓國人咁，系機場到，一大堆咁系電梯跑來跑去，好危險的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2z3q3O9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2z3q3O9.jpg&h=dbdbfa1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m3cWq2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm3cWq2w.jpg&h=65ba226f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0iZReVS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0iZReVS.jpg&h=6cbff5bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HUu53Pe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHUu53Pe.jpg&h=bfb21e55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c5d7eaf74709807e9cb4a1a6d9ebb5ef5cc65d3","tid":1454044,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:03:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ce348cd52660872657bf58ac96b4f29e3c35cc2","tid":1454044,"uid":268927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:07:24.000Z","msg":"有無人知下文如何？"},{"pid":"0dd73cf3bccd04dba4f8dc7301a00c5a